{"tid":132012,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"做消防員既你麻煩入一入黎","createTime":"2017-02-23T13:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T14:10:44.000Z","uid":62499,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c20fb53f8a4f3becea3adf478991069a5932580e","tid":132012,"uid":62499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:25:11.000Z","msg":"小弟做緊份功課，需要各位消防員幫幫手回答幾條問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1。過去的六個月，你消防員的工作中有沒有遇到過特別的事件，關於與上司、同事或下屬溝通？<br />\n2。你作出了甚麼決定/行為來應付事件？<br />\n3。如果你有多一次機會，你會有甚麼不同的回應/反應？<br />\n4。你現在認為你的主管會吩咐你作出怎樣的回應？<br />\n<br />\n可以既話麻煩重覆1-4既問題答多幾次，感謝。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef4181027452c7da36cde1edd1f075738ca21fd","tid":132012,"uid":62499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:30:18.000Z","msg":"推推推推推"},{"pid":"7db78aca708a847278a848765b0f28bee708dfa6","tid":132012,"uid":62499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:37:04.000Z","msg":"連登既消防員去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd5deb200655a4cbde541a54e7ff2c5a95e929c","tid":132012,"uid":62499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a88d593b6eb7d193f7d7d48b54d7c189ada5bf7","tid":132012,"uid":62499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T14:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}